<subSubSection id="99F2651FFFB2FFE8FCCCFE0E4DBBFCFF" pageId="3" pageNumber="96" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="D1573694FFB2FFE8FCCCFE0E4DBBFCFF" blockId="3.[801,1452,471,783]" pageId="3" pageNumber="96">
<emphasis id="E39CEA86FFB2FFE8FCCCFE0E4AFAFE1E" box="[839,920,472,495]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="96">Notes. –</emphasis>
The only original material preserved in G-PREL [G00360112], an uncited specimen from unknown origin, represents a juvenile of 
<taxonomicName id="16E84D17FFB2FFE8FC70FDC14D8AFDDF" authority="L." box="[1019,1256,535,559]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Pteridaceae" genus="Acrostichum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="3" pageNumber="96" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="aureum">
<emphasis id="E39CEA86FFB2FFE8FC70FDC14DABFDDE" box="[1019,1225,535,559]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="96">Acrostichum aureum</emphasis>
L.
</taxonomicName>
, as determined by A.H.G. Alston (label). Aware of this, 
<bibRefCitation id="B5794B65FFB2FFE8FB22FDE14C1DFDBE" author="MORTON" box="[1193,1407,567,591]" firstAuthor="MORTON" journalOrPublisher="Contr. U. S. Natl. Herb." page="316" pageId="3" pageNumber="96" pagination="283 - 396" part="38" refId="ref10010" refString="MORTON, C. V. (1974). William Roxburgh's fern types. Contr. U. S. Natl. Herb. 38: 283 - 396." title="William Roxburgh's fern types" type="journal article" year="1974">MORTON (1974: 316)</bibRefCitation>
was not sure whether this gathering should be considered as the type (“If this really is the type”) and therefore did not designate a 
<typeStatus id="0E538836FFB2FFE8FCECFD414AAAFD5E" box="[871,968,663,687]" pageId="3" pageNumber="96">lectotype</typeStatus>
(
<bibRefCitation id="B5794B65FFB2FFE8FC5CFD414DD1FD5E" author="TURLAND" box="[983,1203,663,687]" etAl="et al." firstAuthor="TURLAND" pageId="3" pageNumber="96" refId="ref10318" refString="TURLAND, N. J., J. H. WIERSEMA, F. R. BARRIE, W. GREUTER, D. L. HAWKSWORTH, P. S. HERENDEEN, S. KNAPP, W. - H. KUSBER, D. - Z. LI, K. MARHOLD, T. W. MAY, J. MCNEILL, A. M. MONRO, J. PRADO, M. J. PRICE &amp; G. F. SMITH (2018). International Code of Nomenclature for algae, fungi, and plants (Shenzhen Code) adopted by the Nineteenth International Botanical Congress Shenzhen, China, July 2017. Regnum Veg. 159." title="International Code of Nomenclature for algae, fungi, and plants (Shenzhen Code) adopted by the Nineteenth International Botanical Congress Shenzhen, China, July 2017" type="proceedings" year="2018">TURLAND et al. 2018</bibRefCitation>
: Art. 7.11). 
<bibRefCitation id="B5794B65FFB2FFE8FAA3FD414A01FD3E" author="MAZUMDAR" firstAuthor="MAZUMDAR" journalOrPublisher="Fern Gaz." pageId="3" pageNumber="96" pagination="91 - 94" part="20" refId="ref9840" refString="MAZUMDAR, J. (2015). Nomenclatural note on Hemionitis arifolia (Pteridaceae). Fern Gaz. 20: 91 - 94." title="Nomenclatural note on Hemionitis arifolia (Pteridaceae)" type="journal article" year="2015">MAZUMDAR (2015)</bibRefCitation>
selected one of the illustrations cited in the protologue (
<bibRefCitation id="B5794B65FFB2FFE8FCA0FD014A8DFD1E" author="RHEEDE" box="[811,1007,727,751]" pageId="3" pageNumber="96" refId="ref10115" refString="RHEEDE [TOT DRAAKESTEIN], H. A. VAN (1678 - 1693). Hortus Indicus Malabaricus. 12 vol. Amsterdam. [vol. 12, 1693]" type="book" year="1693">RHEEDE, 1693: 21</bibRefCitation>
, tab. 10) as 
<typeStatus id="0E538836FFB2FFE8FBF8FD014DBAFD1E" box="[1139,1240,727,751]" pageId="3" pageNumber="96">lectotype</typeStatus>
and designated an epitype to fix the taxonomy of this name.
</paragraph>
